thread.title: Michelle Cheung

author: Michelle Cheung
title: Michelle Cheung
text: I first knew Casetify from its popup store, and that's where I got my first case from Casetify. I got it because I love the watercolour design, but I didn't expect the quality is so good as well. I am the type of person who always drop my phone but Casetify's case is so sturdy that I don't have to worry about breaking my screen anymore. Even the packaging itself is very nice. I really recommend Casetify for anyone who is looking for phone case that got both design and protection, and their phone case is a really good idea for gift too.
